channel.title: Need a website developer
channel.description: I need a urgent website developer to finally get my server going! I've been at it constantly for 3 months. The last step is developing a website so we can put the webclient up so players can finally play, and so I can release the client, setup the highscores, votepages, and stuff so and it'll be 100% ready to go. I have a clear idea of what I want, and it's pretty simple and probably basic, to you web devs out there, but I'm totally inexperienced when it comes to web dev. Please help, ty. If you want more info, or you're willing to help, contact me here, via PM thank you so much.
